<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
  This website (<a href="https://angelomeniconi.co.uk">angelomeniconi.co.uk</a>) respects your privacy. This policy explains what personal data we collect and how we use it.
</p>

<section class="privacy-details">
  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> name, email, and message</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies/analytics:</strong> via Google Analytics (through GTM, only after consent)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <p>
    Personal data is used to respond to inquiries and to analyze site usage to improve the website. Analytics data is anonymous and only collected if cookies are accepted.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    Contact form submissions are sent only to the site owner. Analytics data is collected by Google only if cookies are accepted.
  </p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You can request deletion of your personal data by contacting us.</li>
    <li>You can disable cookies at any time via the cookie banner or browser settings.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For questions about privacy, email: <a href="mailto:angelo.meniconi@gmail.com">angelo.meniconi@gmail.com</a>.
  </p>
</section>
